<%- include('../../partials/header') %>
<%- include('../../partials/navigation') %>

<main class="min-h-screen pt-12 pb-24 bg-white">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
        <nav class="flex space-x-2 mb-10 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400">
            <a href="/knowledge-hub" class="hover:text-brand-blue transition-colors">Knowledge Hub</a>
            <span>/</span>
            <span class="text-gray-900">Compliance</span>
        </nav>

        <!-- H1 Header -->
        <header class="mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-[0.95] uppercase italic">
                The 2026 Guide to <span class="text-brand-blue">Confirmation Statements</span>
            </h1>
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-6 p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-gray-100">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-brand-navy flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[10px] font-black shadow-lg">RM</div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-gray-900 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-tight">Rachel Moore</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Compliance Lead • 6 Min Read</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Key Summary Box -->
        <div class="p-10 bg-brand-navy text-white rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl mb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-full -mr-16 -mt-16 blur-3xl"></div>
            <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-blue mb-6">Key Summary</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <span>Filing is <strong>mandatory</strong> every 12 months for all UK companies.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <span>The deadline is strictly <strong>14 days</strong> from the confirmation date.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-200">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <span>Failing to file results in <strong>company strike-off</strong> and loss of assets.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-xl max-w-none text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
            <!-- Introduction -->
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tighter uppercase italic">Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-900 font-bold mb-12">
                Maintaining a UK company requires more than just high-quality service; it requires unwavering <strong>statutory compliance</strong>. The Confirmation Statement (CS01) is the single most important annual document you will file with Companies House. It is your official declaration that your company's vital signs are accurate and active.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-16 mb-8 tracking-tighter uppercase italic">The Step-by-Step Filing Roadmap</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Step 1: Access and Preparation</h3>
            <p class="mb-6">Begin by gathering your statutory records. You will need your <strong>WebFiling authentication code</strong> or access to an Authorized Corporate Service Provider (ACSP) portal. Ensure you have reviewed your register of members and directors before starting the process.</p>
            
            <!-- Mid-Article CTA -->
            <div class="my-12 p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-[2rem] border border-dashed border-gray-300 text-center">
                <p class="text-sm font-black text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Need a professional to handle your filings?</p>
                <a href="/pricing" class="px-10 py-5 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-2xl text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-brand-blue transition-all inline-block shadow-xl shadow-gray-200">Start Your Formation & Compliance</a>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Step 2: Data Verification</h3>
            <p>During the filing, you must cross-reference and confirm the following data points:</p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-4 my-8">
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"></span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900"><strong>Registered Office Address</strong>: Must be a physical UK location.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"></span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900"><strong>Officer Details</strong>: Directors, secretaries, and their service addresses.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"></span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900"><strong>Share Capital</strong>: Exact breakdown of issued shares and shareholders.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-blue shrink-0"></span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900"><strong>SIC Codes</strong>: Correct classification of your business activity.</span>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Step 3: PSC Identity Verification</h3>
            <p><strong>Critical Update:</strong> As of 2026, all People with Significant Control (PSC) must have <strong>verified identity status</strong> to file a valid Confirmation Statement. This is a non-negotiable legal requirement under the Economic Crime and Corporate Transparency Act.</p>

            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-16 mb-8 tracking-tighter uppercase italic">The Cost of Non-Compliance</h2>
            <p>Failing to submit the CS01 within the 14-day window is a criminal offense. The consequences are severe:</p>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 mt-8 font-bold text-gray-900">
                <li><span class="text-red-600">Criminal Prosecution</span> of company directors.</li>
                <li><span class="text-red-600">Company Dissolution</span>: Companies House will assume the business is no longer trading.</li>
                <li><span class="text-red-600">Asset Forfeiture</span>: Any assets held by a dissolved company transfer to the Crown.</li>
            </ol>

            <!-- Final CTA -->
            <div class="mt-24 p-12 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-[3.5rem] relative overflow-hidden text-center shadow-3xl not-prose">
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-blue/5 rounded-full -ml-32 -mb-32 blur-3xl"></div>
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter uppercase italic">Stay Compliant, Stay Focused</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 text-lg font-medium max-w-xl mx-auto">Focus on scaling your business while our experts handle your statutory filings and Companies House liaison.</p>
                <a href="/pricing" class="px-12 py-6 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-2xl text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-white hover:text-brand-navy transition-all inline-block shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/20">
                    Start Your Formation & Compliance
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</main>

<%- include('../../partials/footer') %>
